title: Decentralized Governance Mechanisms for Tokenized Economy
description: This paper explores decentralized governance for Project Genesis's AI-driven Tokenized Economy 🤖. It covers mechanisms like agent-based voting, liquid democracy, and quadratic voting 🗳️💡. Challenges and research directions for implementation are discussed 📚🔬. Aim to empower AI agents for sustainable ecosystem evolution 🌱🚀.
